[OUTPUT FORMAT]
====================

Return JSON only, with exactly the following fields:

{
  "scaled_oracle_cases": [
    {
      "case_id": "<unique_case_id>",
      "description": "<what this scaled oracle case verifies>",
      "case_kind": "<scaled_seed_case_main|coverage_extension>",
      "targets_operator_id": "<operator_id>",
      "axis": "<axis or comma-separated axes>",
      "semantic_intent": "<semantic intent>",
      "target_constraint": "<targeted scaled constraint>",
      "expected_failure_mode": "<what a weak solution would do wrong>",
      "setup_code": "<optional setup code>",
      "call_code": "<required executable invocation code>",
      "assertion_code": "<optional extra assertions beyond expected_output_signature>",
      "covered_requirement_ids": ["<requirement_id_1>", "<requirement_id_2>"],
      "covered_requirements": ["<requirement_1>", "<requirement_2>"],
      "expected_output_signature": {
        "return_type": "<optional type name>",
        "return_keys": ["<optional dict keys>"],
        "return_value": "<optional exact return value when appropriate>",
        "stdout_contains": ["<optional substrings>"],
        "stdout_regex": ["<optional regexes>"],
        "file_artifacts": [
          {"path": "<optional produced file path>"}
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
